## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f58ee-104">此属性将标记基础结构用于执行 WMI 获取操作的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f58ee-104">This attribute marks the method that the infrastructure uses to perform the WMI get operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f58ee-105">该方法必须采用相应的 WMI 类的键值作为参数并返回关联的 WMI 类实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f58ee-105">The method must take the key values of the corresponding WMI class as parameters and return the associated instance of the WMI class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f58ee-106">**重要**方法参数必须与类的密钥参数具有完全相同的名称和类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f58ee-106">**Important** The method parameters must have exactly the same name and type as the key parameters of the class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f58ee-107">由标识键参数。<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementKeyAttribute></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f58ee-107">The key parameters are identified by the .<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementKeyAttribute></span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f58ee-108">属性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f58ee-108">attribute</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f58ee-109">该方法必须将值分配给类的所有已插入检测点的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f58ee-109">The method must assign values to all instrumented properties of the class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f58ee-110">当 WMI 提供程序扩展基础结构需要此绑定功能时，它将先搜索此特性的构造函数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f58ee-110">When the WMI Provider Extensions infrastructure requires this binding functionality, it first searches for a constructor with this attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f58ee-111">如果找不到，它则搜索返回的 WMI 类类型的静态方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f58ee-111">If none is found, it then searches for a static method that returns the WMI class type.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f58ee-112">此属性的目标必须是一种方法或静态方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f58ee-112">The target of this attribute must be either a method or a static method.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="f58ee-113">下面的示例演示如何使用 ManagementBind 属性标记的类构造函数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f58ee-113">The following example shows how to use the ManagementBind attribute to mark the constructor of a class.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Use the ManagementBind attribute to specify that this constructor  
// is used to attach a class instance to a specific WMI  
// instance. The constructor should set the values of the  
// key properties of the WMI instance.  
[ManagementBind]  
public ClassConstructor(int Id)  
{  
     // Set this class instance to a specific instance  
     // by assigning property values and   
     // giving unique values to the key properties.   
}  
```
